# .cursorrules
- Framework: Next.js 14+ (App Router), Typescript, Tailwind CSS.
- Style: "Medical Fintech" aesthetic. Clean, large fonts, whites, blues (#2563EB), and Slate grays.
- Architecture: Client-side logic for the calculator. API Routes for external webhooks.
- Tooling: Use 'lucide-react' for icons, 'zod' for validation, 'react-hook-form' for inputs.
- Constraints: NO DATABASE setup (Prisma/Supabase) yet. Use the provided API route structure to send data to Make.com.
- Language: Portuguese (PT-BR) ONLY for UI text.